([Step], [Title], [Body], [TextPrompt], [VideoUrl], [PdfUrl], [VideoName], [Category], [IsActive], [CreatorId], [CreatedDateTimeUTC], [LastModifiedByUserId], [LastModifiedDateTimeUTC])
VALUES
(1, 'How to cope with anger', 'Anger is a normal and healthy emotion, but sometimes it can get out of control and cause problems in your life. In this video, you will learn some strategies to manage your anger effectively and constructively.', 'What are some situations that make you angry?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/362123047', NULL, 'Anger Management Techniques', 0, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(2, 'How to express your anger in a healthy way', 'Anger is not always a bad thing, as long as you express it in a healthy and respectful way. In this video, you will learn some tips to communicate your anger assertively and avoid aggression or passive-aggression.', 'How do you usually express your anger?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/292395064', NULL, 'How to Express Your Anger in a Healthy Way', 0, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(3, 'How to calm down when you are angry', 'When you are angry, you may feel like you are losing control and want to lash out at others. However, this can make things worse and damage your relationships. In this video, you will learn some techniques to calm down when you are angry and regain your composure.', 'What are some things that help you calm down?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/362134114', NULL, 'How to Calm Down When You Are Angry', 0, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(4, 'How to cope with anger triggers', 'Anger triggers are the things that make you angry, such as people, situations, or events. They can vary from person to person and depend on your personality, mood, and stress level. In this video, you will learn how to identify your anger triggers and cope with them effectively.', 'What are some of your anger triggers?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/362129741', NULL, 'How to Cope with Anger Triggers', 0, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(5, 'How to prevent anger from ruining your life', 'Anger can be a powerful and positive force, but it can also be destructive and harmful if you let it take over your life. In this video, you will learn how to prevent anger from ruining your life and affecting your health, happiness, and relationships.', 'How has anger affected your life?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/362134114', NULL, 'How to Prevent Anger from Ruining Your Life', 0, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(6, 'How to deal with anxiety', 'Anxiety is a common and natural response to stress or uncertainty, but sometimes it can interfere with your daily functioning and well-being. In this video, you will learn some tips to reduce your anxiety and cope with your worries.', 'What are some things that make you anxious?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/362707415', NULL, 'How to Calm Down During a Panic Attack', 1, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(7, 'How to overcome social anxiety', 'Social anxiety is a fear of being judged, rejected, or embarrassed in social situations. It can make you avoid social interactions or feel nervous and uncomfortable around others. In this video, you will learn some ways to overcome social anxiety and boost your confidence.', 'How do you feel in social situations?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/285885756', NULL, 'How to Overcome Social Anxiety', 1, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(8, 'How to cope with anxiety attacks', 'Anxiety attacks are sudden and intense episodes of fear or panic that can make you feel like you are losing control or dying. They can be triggered by stress, trauma, or specific situations. In this video, you will learn how to cope with anxiety attacks and prevent them from happening again.', 'Have you ever experienced an anxiety attack?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/362725307', NULL, 'How to Cope with Anxiety Attacks', 1, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(9, 'How to cope with generalized anxiety disorder (GAD)', 'Generalized anxiety disorder (GAD) is a chronic and excessive worry about various aspects of life, such as health, work, family, or finances. It can cause physical and mental symptoms, such as restlessness, fatigue, irritability, or insomnia. In this video, you will learn how to cope with GAD and manage your worry.', 'What are some things that you worry about?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/362783278', NULL, 'How to Cope with Generalized Anxiety Disorder (GAD)', 1, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(10, 'How to cope with phobias', 'Phobias are irrational and intense fears of specific objects or situations, such as spiders, heights, or flying. They can cause extreme anxiety and avoidance behavior, and interfere with your daily life. In this video, you will learn how to cope with phobias and overcome your fears.', 'What are some of your phobias?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/288040319', NULL, 'How to Cope with Phobias', 1, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(11, 'How to overcome depression', 'Depression is a serious and common mental health condition that affects your mood, thoughts, and behavior. It can make you feel sad, hopeless, and lose interest in things you used to enjoy. In this video, you will learn some ways to fight depression and improve your mood.', 'What are some activities that make you happy?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/321847129', NULL, 'How to Beat Depression', 2, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(12, 'How to cope with bipolar disorder', 'Bipolar disorder is a mental health condition that causes extreme mood swings, from highs (mania or hypomania) to lows (depression). It can affect your energy, activity, sleep, and judgment. In this video, you will learn how to cope with bipolar disorder and manage your mood.', 'How do you cope with your mood swings?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/285009245', NULL, 'How to Cope with Bipolar Disorder', 2, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(13, 'How to cope with seasonal affective disorder (SAD)', 'Seasonal affective disorder (SAD) is a type of depression that occurs during certain seasons, usually winter. It can make you feel low, lethargic, and unmotivated. In this video, you will learn how to cope with SAD and brighten your mood.', 'How do you feel during the winter months?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/362723006', NULL, 'How to Cope with Seasonal Affective Disorder (SAD)', 2, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(14, 'How to cope with postpartum depression', 'Postpartum depression is a type of depression that affects some women after giving birth. It can make you feel sad, anxious, guilty, or hopeless. It can also affect your ability to bond with your baby and care for yourself. In this video, you will learn how to cope with postpartum depression and seek help.', 'How do you feel after having a baby?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/289760468', NULL, 'How to Cope with Postpartum Depression', 2, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(15, 'How to cope with dysthymia', 'Dysthymia is a chronic and mild form of depression that lasts for at least two years. It can make you feel low, pessimistic, and unmotivated. It can also affect your self-esteem, relationships, and work performance. In this video, you will learn how to cope with dysthymia and enhance your well-being.', 'How do you cope with your low mood?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/362724629', NULL, 'How to cope with your low mood', 2, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()), 
(16, 'How to cope with guilt', 'Guilt is a feeling of regret or remorse for something you did or didn''t do, or for hurting someone else. Guilt can be helpful when it motivates you to make amends or change your behavior, but it can also be harmful when it leads to self-criticism or shame. In this video, you will learn some ways to cope with guilt and forgive yourself.', 'What are some things that make you feel guilty?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/751301521', NULL, 'How to Let Go of Guilt', 3, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(17, 'How to cope with survivor''s guilt', 'Survivor''s guilt is a feeling of guilt for surviving a traumatic event or situation when others did not. It can make you feel responsible, angry, or unworthy. It can also affect your mental health and well-being. In this video, you will learn how to cope with survivor''s guilt and heal from your trauma.', 'Have you ever experienced survivor''s guilt?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/283520345', NULL, 'How to Cope with Survivor''s Guilt', 3, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(18, 'How to cope with moral guilt', 'Moral guilt is a feeling of guilt for violating your own moral standards or values. It can make you feel ashamed, remorseful, or conflicted. It can also motivate you to correct your mistakes and improve yourself. In this video, you will learn how to cope with moral guilt and restore your integrity.', 'What are some of your moral values?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/751307361', NULL, 'How to Cope with Moral Guilt', 3, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(19, 'How to cope with false guilt', 'False guilt is a feeling of guilt for something you are not responsible for or did not do wrong. It can make you feel undeserving, insecure, or powerless. It can also result from unrealistic expectations, manipulation, or abuse. In this video, you will learn how to cope with false guilt and reclaim your truth.', 'What are some examples of false guilt?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/751310043', NULL, 'How to Cope with False Guilt', 3, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(20, 'How to cope with guilt and regret', 'Guilt and regret are feelings of sorrow or disappointment for something you did or didn''t do in the past. They can make you feel stuck, depressed, or hopeless. They can also prevent you from moving on and enjoying your present and future. In this video, you will learn how to cope with guilt and regret and let go of the past.', 'What are some things that you regret?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/751305456', NULL, 'How to Cope with Guilt and Regret', 3, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(21, 'How to use the ABCs technique', 'The ABCs technique is a cognitive-behavioral therapy (CBT) tool that can help you change your negative thoughts and emotions. The ABCs stand for Activating event, Beliefs, Consequences, and Disputing. In this video, you will learn how to use the ABCs technique to challenge your irrational beliefs and replace them with more realistic and positive ones.', 'What are some examples of irrational beliefs that you have?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/751310043', NULL, 'How to Use the ABCs Technique', 4, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(22, 'How to use the SMART goals technique', 'The SMART goals technique is a tool that can help you set and achieve your goals. The SMART stands for Specific, Measurable, Achievable, Relevant, and Time-bound. In this video, you will learn how to use the SMART goals technique to make your goals clear, realistic, and motivating.', 'What are some of your goals?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/288040319', NULL, 'How to Use the SMART Goals Technique', 4, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(23, 'How to use the mindfulness technique', 'The mindfulness technique is a tool that can help you focus on the present moment and reduce stress and anxiety. Mindfulness is the practice of paying attention to your thoughts, feelings, sensations, and surroundings without judgment or distraction. In this video, you will learn how to use the mindfulness technique to improve your mental and physical health.', 'What are some benefits of mindfulness?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/751305456', NULL, 'How to Use the Mindfulness Technique', 4, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(24, 'How to use the gratitude technique', 'The gratitude technique is a tool that can help you appreciate what you have and increase your happiness and well-being. Gratitude is the feeling of thankfulness for the people, things, and experiences in your life. In this video, you will learn how to use the gratitude technique to boost your mood and positivity.', 'What are some things that you are grateful for?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/751301521', NULL, 'How to Use the Gratitude Technique', 4, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE()),
(25, 'How to use the reframing technique', 'The reframing technique is a tool that can help you change your perspective and attitude towards a situation or problem. Reframing is the process of finding a different or positive way of looking at something that is causing you stress or distress. In this video, you will learn how to use the reframing technique to cope with challenges and opportunities.', 'What are some situations that you can reframe?', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/283520345', NULL, 'How to Use the Reframing Technique', 4, 1, 1, GETUTCDATE(), 1, GETUTCDATE());
